    → <a href="/cases/">实战案例</a> → 浏览器自动化
  </div>

  <article class="case-study">
    <header>
      <div class="tag">效率神器</div>
      <h1>🌐 浏览器自动化：让 AI 帮你处理重复性办公任务</h1>
      <p class="lead">自动填写表单、批量下载文件、跨网站数据整理...解放你的双手！</p>
    </header>

    <section class="content">
      <h2>🎯 适用场景</h2>
      <div class="scenarios">
        <div class="scenario">
          <span class="scenario-icon">📊</span>
          <h3>数据收集</h3>
          <p>从多个网站抓取产品价格、竞品信息、市场数据</p>
        </div>
        <div class="scenario">
          <span class="scenario-icon">📝</span>
          <h3>表单填写</h3>
          <p>批量提交报名表、申请表、信息登记等重复表单</p>
        </div>
        <div class="scenario">
          <span class="scenario-icon">📥</span>
          <h3>文件下载</h3>
          <p>自动下载日报、周报、月度报表等定期文件</p>
        </div>
        <div class="scenario">
          <span class="scenario-icon">🔄</span>
          <h3>数据同步</h3>
          <p>在多个系统间同步客户信息、订单数据等</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2>🛠️ 前置条件</h2>
      <div class="requirements">
        <div class="req-item">
          <span class="req-icon">✅</span>
          <div>
            <strong>OpenClaw v1.5.0+</strong>
            <small>支持浏览器自动化功能</small>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="req-item">
          <span class="req-icon">✅</span>
          <div>
            <strong>Node.js 22+</strong>
            <small>推荐 Node 24</small>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="req-item">
          <span class="req-icon">✅</span>
          <div>
            <strong>浏览器</strong>
            <small>Chrome / Edge / Firefox</small>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2>📚 实战案例 1：自动收集竞品价格</h2>
      
      <div class="example">
        <h3>场景描述</h3>
        <p>你需要每天监控 3 个电商平台的竞品价格，手动查看耗时 30 分钟。现在让 AI 帮你自动完成！</p>
        
        <h3>实现步骤</h3>
        <div class="steps">
          <div class="step">
            <span class="step-num">1</span>
            <div>
              <h4>创建浏览器脚本</h4>
              <pre><code>// scripts/price-collector.cjs
const { browser } = require('openclaw');

async function collectPrices() {
  const products = ['产品 A', '产品 B', '产品 C'];
  const platforms = [
    { name: '淘宝', url: 'https://taobao.com' },
    { name: '京东', url: 'https://jd.com' },
    { name: '拼多多', url: 'https://pinduoduo.com' }
  ];
  
  const results = [];
  
  for (const platform of platforms) {
    await browser.navigate(platform.url);
    
    for (const product of products) {
      // 搜索产品
      await browser.type('[name="q"]', product);
      await browser.press('Enter');
      await browser.wait(2000);
      
      // 提取价格
      const price = await browser.evaluate(() => {
        const el = document.querySelector('.price');
        return el ? el.textContent : 'N/A';
      });
      
      results.push({
        platform: platform.name,
        product,
        price,
        timestamp: new Date().toISOString()
      });
    }
  }
  
  // 保存结果
  const fs = require('fs');
  fs.writeFileSync(
    'price-data.json',
    JSON.stringify(results, null, 2)
  );
  
  console.log('✅ 价格收集完成！');
}

module.exports = collectPrices;</code></pre>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="step">
            <span class="step-num">2</span>
            <div>
              <h4>配置定时任务</h4>
              <p>在 <code>HEARTBEAT.md</code> 中添加：</p>
              <pre><code># 每日竞品价格收集
- 每天早上 9:00 自动收集竞品价格
- 保存到 price-data.json
- 如果价格变化超过 10%，发送提醒</code></pre>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="step">
            <span class="step-num">3</span>
            <div>
              <h4>运行测试</h4>
              <pre><code># 手动运行一次
node scripts/price-collector.cjs

# 查看输出
cat price-data.json</code></pre>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <h3>效果对比</h3>
        <div class="comparison">
